      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Almudron: Fashion Victim",
        "Client": "Hamon the Blacksmith",
        "Description": "Rondine showed me a pair of\r\ntight pants from some far-off\r\ncountry. I don\u0027t know fashion,\r\nbut I know a pair of sturdy\r\npants when I see \u0027em! Complete\r\nmy request, and I\u0027ll give you\r\nthe materials to forge \u0027em.",
        "Target": "Hunt an Almudron",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Almudron, victime de la mode",
        "Client": "Hamon le forgeron",
        "Description": "Rondine m\u0027a montr\u00E9 un dr\u00F4le de\r\npantalon d\u0027un pays \u00E9tranger.\r\nJ\u0027y connais rien \u00E0 la mode,\r\nmais ce pantalon, c\u0027\u00E9tait du\r\nsolide ! Occupe-toi de ma\r\nrequ\u00EAte et je te donnerai le\r\nmat\u00E9riel pour le forger.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Almudron",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Almudron, vittima della moda",
        "Client": "Hamon il fabbro",
        "Description": "Rondine mi ha mostrato un paio\r\ndi pantaloni molto attillati da\r\nuna terra lontana. Non me ne\r\nintendo di moda, ma so\r\nriconoscere dei pantaloni\r\nresistenti! Aiutami e ti dar\u00F2\r\ni materiali per crearli.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Almudron",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Almudron: Modeopfer",
        "Client": "Hamon der Schmied",
        "Description": "Rondine hat mir eine Hose aus\r\neinem fernen Land gezeigt. Von\r\nMode hab ich keine Ahnung,\r\naber die Hose sah echt robust\r\naus! Erf\u00FClle meine Bitte, dann\r\ngebe ich dir die Materialien\r\nf\u00FCr die Hose.",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Almudron.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Almudron, v\u00EDctima de la moda",
        "Client": "Hamon el herrero",
        "Description": "Rondine me ha ense\u00F1ado unos\r\npantalones ce\u00F1idos de un pa\u00EDs\r\nlejano. No s\u00E9 de moda, \u00A1pero\r\ns\u00E9 reconocer unos pantalones\r\nresistentes! Si completas mi\r\npetici\u00F3n, te doy lo necesario\r\npara que los puedas forjar.",
        "Target": "Caza un Almudron",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
